<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>ONNX Runtime on Mi&amp;Bee Blog</title><link>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/tags/onnx-runtime/</link><description>Recent content in ONNX Runtime on Mi&amp;Bee Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><managingEditor>蓝宝石的傻话</managingEditor><lastBuildDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/tags/onnx-runtime/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>YOLO Golang 部署实战</title><link>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/posts/aihelper/yolo-golang-deployment/</link><pubDate>Tue, 26 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/posts/aihelper/yolo-golang-deployment/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="第-8-章golang-使用-yolo-完整教程"&gt;第 8 章：Golang 使用 YOLO 完整教程&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Go 语言凭借其高性能、低内存占用、原生并发特性，成为工业级 YOLO 部署的首选语言之一。本章将详细介绍 Go 生态中 YOLO 的完整实现方案。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>YOLO Rust 部署实战</title><link>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/posts/aihelper/yolo-rust-deployment/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.mickeyzzc.tech/posts/aihelper/yolo-rust-deployment/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="第-9-章rust-使用-yolo-完整教程"&gt;第 9 章：Rust 使用 YOLO 完整教程&lt;/h2&gt;
